Steven Ernest Bernard Zaillian -LRB- born January 30 , 1953 -RRB- is an Armenian-American screenwriter , director , film editor , producer , and founder of Film Rites , a film production company .
He won an Academy Award , a Golden Globe Award and a BAFTA Award for his screenplay Schindler 's List -LRB- 1993 -RRB- and he has been nominated for Awakenings , Gangs of New York and Moneyball .
He was also presented with the Distinguished Screenwriter Award at the 2009 Austin Film Festival and the Laurel Award for Screenwriting Achievement from the Writers Guild of America in 2011 .